{"color":"DEFAULT","isTrashed":false,"isPinned":false,"isArchived":false,"textContent":"Pull up machine - 90lbs 10, 80 lbs 10, 70lbs>80lbs 4>5...2HF\nLat pulldown - 87 lbs 12, 125 lbs 10, 125lbs+10lbs>125lbs>87lbs 5>5>5 fast...5 slow*...1 hold 5 sec**\nReverse pec deck fly - 60 lbs 10, 70lbs 12, 11F\nChest-supported rows - 75 lbs 12, 87 lbs 10, 100lbs>87lbs 7>4\nDumbbell shrugs/Lat raise - 25lbs/15lbs 15/12, 30lbs/15lbs 15/15, 15/15\nBarbell rows - bar+2x25lbs 12, bar+2x(25lbs+2.5lbs) 10, bar+2x(25lbs+2x2.5lbs) 9F\nFacepull - 66lbs 12, 77 lbs 10, 10\nPreachers curl - 20 lbs 10, 30lbs>20lbs 5>5\n>5, 30lbs>20lbs>10lbs 4>3>10\nForearm curl/Reverse forearm curl - 15lbs/10lbs 15/10, 15/12, 15/12\nBicep curl - 15 lbs 10~10, 15 lbs>10lbs 6...2~8>6...2~8 \n\nNotes:\n* - not good form by the end\n** - not good form from the start, di ko na mababa abot chest \n\nWeight : 78.5 kg\n","title":"October 16, 2025","userEditedTimestampUsec":1760624505542000,"createdTimestampUsec":1760611150614000,"textContentHtml":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Pull up machine - 90lbs 10, 80 lbs 10, 70lbs&gt;80lbs 4&gt;5...2HF<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Lat pulldown - 87 lbs 12, 125 lbs 10, 125lbs+10lbs&gt;125lbs&gt;87lbs 5&gt;5&gt;5 fast...5 slow*...1 hold 5 sec**<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#00